Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.45,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c00008C\1c82C0FF}虹がかかるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.91,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c00008C\1c82C0FF}そんな日が来るさ
